portfolio.title: Big Buck Bunny
portfolio.reason: Blender Foundation initiated this open movie project. A small team (7) of the best 3D artists and developers in the Blender community have been invited to come together to work in Amsterdam from October 2007 until April 2008 on completing a short 3D animation movie.

portfolio.title: Video Fail Loading

portfolio.reason: Sometimes the video is not available or the link is broken. The website has no timeout and will simply wait for the video to load indefinitely.
